<ul class="gs_text" style="margin-top:20px;margin-left:35px;margin-right:15px">
	<li style="text-align:left">Security foot patrols throughout the exterior and interior of the shopping centre 7 days a week, 365 days a year</li>
	<li style="text-align:left">Emergency first response for events such as medical aid. All Bay Centre security staff are certified in first aid, including CPR, Defibrillator and oxygen therapy</li>
